  <brief_title>Prevention of Akute Kidney Injury, Hearttransplant, ANP</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prevention of Akute Kidney Injury With Human Atrial Natriuretic Peptide in Patients Undergoing Heart Transplant.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
