  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  De novo Htx.

          -  Preoperative GFR &gt; 30ml/min/1,73m2.

          -  &gt;18 years old.

          -  Written consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Multi organ transplantation or previous heart transplant.

          -  ECMO

          -  Donor age &gt; 70 years.

          -  Dialysis.

          -  ABO-incompatible organ.

          -  Donor heart ischemia time &gt; 6 tim.

          -  Known kidney disease.

          -  Other planed study within 2 mounth.
      </textblock>
